If directional shadows range is set smaller than camera view range there is full dark area behind shadows range don't know if this solves and can't try it but i believe setting ShadowBuffer texture edge to white should solve this.

glTexParameteri(GL_TEXTURE_2D,GL_TEXTURE_WRAP_S, GL_CLAMP_TO_BORDER);
